<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Smart Student System</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="main.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px; /* Adding padding to body */
    }

    .quote-container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background-color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(143, 146, 179, 0.1);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto; /* Center horizontally */
      margin-top: 150px; /* Add margin top */
      transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }

    .quote {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .author {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #777;
    }
   
    .links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap; /* Allow buttons to wrap to the next line on smaller screens */
      gap: 10px; /* Adjust the gap between buttons as needed */
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .links a {
      text-decoration: none; /* To remove any default link styling */
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navigation and sidebar includes -->
  <%- include ('NavBar.ejs') -%>
  <div id="wrapper">
    <%- include ('SideBar.ejs') -%>

    <!-- Quote section -->
    <div class="quote-container">
      <div class="quote">
        <p>Welcome to our smart registration system! Your journey starts here, where dreams meet dedication and every course shapes a brighter future.</p>
        <p>Letâ€™s embark on this educational adventure together with enthusiasm and determination.</p>
        <div class="author">
          <p>-college name</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="links">
      <a href="/CourseLoad"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Check Your Timetable</button></a>
      <a href="/recommender"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Register Your Courses with AI</button></a>
      <a href="/transcript"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">View Your Grades</button></a>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="sidebar.js"></script>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
